flowPatch` silently swallowed EACCES permission errors. Now throws on permission errors, null only for missing files.","+- **MEDIUM fixed:** Empty catch clause in embedded workflow loading discarded original error message.","+- **MEDIUM fixed:** No test for `resolveWorkflow({ name: 'custom' })` path. Added.","+- **LOW (not fixed):** `deepMerge` duplicated in agent-resolver.ts and workflow-parser.ts.","+- **LOW (not fixed):** Custom workflow detection re-reads file that `parseWorkflow` also reads (minor I/O waste).","+- Coverage: 96.75% overall, all 163 files above 80%.","+","+## Token Report — code-review","+- Total tool calls: 18","+- By tool: Bash: 6, Read: 8, Edit: 6, Grep: 2, Glob: 1, Skill: 1","+- Largest Bash outputs: `npm run test:unit --reporter=verbose` (~80 lines), `git diff --name-only` (~20 lines)","+- Files read: 10 unique, 11 total reads","+- Redundant operations: none"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
