ce semantics, user-before-project ordering, schema validation after merge, referential integrity after merge\n\n## Files Verified\n\n| File | Exists | Key Exports |\n|------|--------|-------------|\n| `src/lib/workflow-parser.ts` | YES | `resolveWorkflow`, `loadWorkflowPatch`, `mergeWorkflowPatch`, `WorkflowPatch`, `parseWorkflow`, `WorkflowParseError` |\n| `src/lib/__tests__/workflow-parser.test.ts` | YES | 39 tests (20 pre-existing + 19 new) |\n| `src/commands/run.ts` | YES | Uses `resolveWorkflow({ cwd: projectDir })` |\n| `templates/workflows/default.yaml` | YES | Embedded default workflow |\n\n## Final Result\n\n**ALL_PASS (10/10 ACs)**\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2756,"cache_read_input_tokens":41861,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2756,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01XJQ88jMzpe5HTH3L7cTEQ4","session_id":"b82e0b02-3413-404d-8b3c-c5e48f86089c","uuid":"e68ddfe4-a6a1-449f-b59f-77a3bac3f704"}
